<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 09:13:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>路透调查显示，随着消费下滑，中国第二季度GDP复苏可能失去动力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-gdp-recovery-likely-lost-steam-q2-consumption-sags-2024-07-10/</link><description>由于消费需求低迷，中国经济第二季度同比增长可能为 5.1%，较前三个月的强劲开局有所放缓，这使得人们对北京需要推出更多刺激措施的预期仍不减。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 08:44:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-gdp-recovery-likely-lost-steam-q2-consumption-sags-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国加强对四大会计师事务所的审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-dials-up-scrutiny-big-four-audit-firms-after-evergrande-probe-sources-say-2024-07-10/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，中国财政部正在对四大审计公司为本土企业所做的工作进行更严格的检查，原因是担心审计机构在发现企业不当行为方面做得不够。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 08:41:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-dials-up-scrutiny-big-four-audit-firms-after-evergrande-probe-sources-say-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>副部长表示波兰将采取必要措施结束白俄罗斯边境危机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/poland-will-do-what-is-needed-end-belarus-border-crisis-says-deputy-minister-2024-07-10/</link><description>一名国防部副部长表示，波兰将尽一切努力解决其与白俄罗斯边境的移民危机，华沙正在权衡可能包括关闭边境在内的选择。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 08:40:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/poland-will-do-what-is-needed-end-belarus-border-crisis-says-deputy-minister-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>商务部称中方将调查欧盟调查是否构成贸易壁垒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-investigate-if-eu-probes-constitute-trade-barriers-says-commerce-ministry-2024-07-10/</link><description>中国商务部周三表示，中国将审查欧盟对中国企业的调查是否构成“贸易壁垒”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 08:17:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-investigate-if-eu-probes-constitute-trade-barriers-says-commerce-ministry-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾参议院调查市长涉嫌与中国犯罪行为及其公民身份的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-senate-probes-mayors-alleged-ties-chinese-crime-her-citizenship-2024-07-10/</link><description>周三，菲律宾参议院在一次听证会上威胁要以藐视法庭罪逮捕一名小镇市长，调查她涉嫌与中国犯罪集团的关系，该案在马尼拉和北京之间的紧张关系中引起了全国的关注。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 06:39:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-senate-probes-mayors-alleged-ties-chinese-crime-her-citizenship-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，由于新的关税担忧，中国六月出口增长更快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-seen-rising-more-quickly-june-amid-fresh-tariff-fears-2024-07-10/</link><description>6月份，中国的出口可能会以十五个月以来最快的速度增长，因为制造商预计中国主要出口市场将越来越多地征收关税，因此提前发货。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 06:03:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-seen-rising-more-quickly-june-amid-fresh-tariff-fears-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国西藏与尼泊尔边境附近暴风雨导致130多人被困</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/storms-trap-more-than-130-near-chinas-border-with-tibet-2024-07-10/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，周三，连续降雨引发山体滑坡和洪水，导致道路交通中断，包括游客在内的 130 多人被困在中国与尼泊尔崎岖的喜马拉雅边境附近的西藏。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 03:23:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/storms-trap-more-than-130-near-chinas-border-with-tibet-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>台湾称，中国航母在前往太平洋演习的途中经过菲律宾附近</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-chinese-aircraft-carrier-carrying-out-drills-western-pacific-2024-07-10/</link><description>台湾国防部长周三表示，中国航母山东号在前往太平洋演习的途中经过菲律宾北部附近，台北报道称有数十架战机加入该舰进行演习。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 02:20:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-chinese-aircraft-carrier-carrying-out-drills-western-pacific-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>美联储九月降息机会增加，股市上涨，美元坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-10/</link><description>美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔前一天就通胀问题发表谨慎但令人鼓舞的言论，提高了人们对美国即将降息的预期，周三股市上涨，美元走强。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 01:47:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>需求疲软，中国6月消费者通胀未达预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-consumer-prices-rise-less-than-expected-june-2024-07-10/</link><description>6月份，中国消费者价格连续第五个月上涨，但未达预期，而生产者价格通缩持续存在，尽管世界第二大经济体采取了支持措施，但国内需求仍陷入缓慢复苏的轨道。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 01:45:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-consumer-prices-rise-less-than-expected-june-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>美元因鲍威尔的谨慎而犹豫不决；新西兰联储利率暗示后新西兰元下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-powell-caution-kiwi-bides-time-before-rates-decision-2024-07-10/</link><description>由于美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔的谨慎语气抑制了风险情绪，美元周三交投于三周低点附近，而在新西兰央行表示看到降息潜力后，新西兰元下跌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 01:05:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-powell-caution-kiwi-bides-time-before-rates-decision-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>由于美国海湾供应担忧缓解以及中国通胀疲弱，油价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-rebounds-us-stockpiles-drop-interest-rate-cut-outlook-brightens-2024-07-10/</link><description>由于飓风贝里尔的影响消散，且通胀数据突显最大原油进口国中国的消费需求持续疲软，油价周三下跌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 01:01:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-rebounds-us-stockpiles-drop-interest-rate-cut-outlook-brightens-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警称“允许”菲律宾撤离南海病人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-coast-guard-says-allowed-philippines-evacuate-sick-person-schina-sea-2024-07-10/</link><description>中国海警表示，基于人道主义理由，“允许”菲律宾撤离一名在仁爱礁搁浅的生锈军舰上患病的人员，马尼拉海警则称这一说法“荒谬”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 00:31:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-coast-guard-says-allowed-philippines-evacuate-sick-person-schina-sea-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国平安计划发行高达50亿美元的可转换债券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/chinas-ping-an-eyes-up-5-bln-convertible-bond-sources-say-2024-07-10/</link><description>据两位直接了解情况的消息人士透露，中国平安保险正在考虑发行价值高达 50 亿美元的可转换债券。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 00:21:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/chinas-ping-an-eyes-up-5-bln-convertible-bond-sources-say-2024-07-10/</guid></item><item><title>Shein 承诺在潜在 IPO 之前投资英国和欧洲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-pledges-invest-uk-europe-ahead-potential-ipo-2024-07-09/</link><description>快时尚零售商 Shein 表示，将在五年内在英国和欧洲投资 2.5 亿欧元（合 2.71 亿美元），以应对对其从中国工厂直接向世界各地购物者空运廉价服装和配饰的模式的批评。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:02:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-pledges-invest-uk-europe-ahead-potential-ipo-2024-07-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>